### Xpiano API Tests

### 1. Welcome endpoint
GET http://localhost:3000/

### 2. Get all pianos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pianos

### 3. Get piano by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pianos/1

### 4. Get pianos with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pianos?category=Grand&minRating=4.5

### 5. Get statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pianos/stats

